{"h29b3ad66gfa98g4c7egb333gb742001171f0": ["*You've tried everything - the chains still hold you.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinPriest_Chains.html", "d881d2d9-1b26-d6ef-6b42-ab27c50816af"], "h26183db1gd594g4a0agb6f2gf2f908f2920b": ["*You test the weight of the chains, looking for weak points.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinPriest_Chains.html", "d7a401ac-26d3-266a-b9cb-e70da196976c"], "h7a65f3a9g75a5g4951gbb65gd89c14b5374a": ["<i>Use the priestess' key.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinPriest_Chains.html", "9cf8e2fc-de2e-52e4-407f-066a37fdb5b8"], "h7edd90c8g4ed0g4ffbgb61fg6fa5db162c40": ["*The lock opens.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinPriest_Chains.html", "2a9705a7-2e1d-78bf-05d0-50082b3a6b87"], "hac4ba490g56a7g427dg8585g3384ac30a9a8": ["<i>Dislocate your wrist, and wriggle free.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinPriest_Chains.html", "cbb0e514-3ba2-2c4e-d4e8-c5165f9f023f"], "h52fd46f0gfdf2g469fga104g05651cd79b7f": ["<i>Inhale deeply, then tear the chains apart.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinPriest_Chains.html", "3510f471-336b-c7f3-9821-6e8829dbbff0"], "h512263cfgabaeg430cg825ag9d5ff1933adb": ["*The chains snap as you expand your chest.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinPriest_Chains.html", "ba767a11-ad97-9206-7afd-96a28c2a0119"], "h9ce514f3g3855g4f3ag960dg6d20a1f9f980": ["<i>Tense your muscles, straining against the chains.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinPriest_Chains.html", "91d8ae5e-afe3-fd56-cbcf-6892941c419e"], "hf7261331gca9dg46ccgac63gb19c47c16613": ["*Your muscles burn with the effort, but the chains hold strong.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinPriest_Chains.html", "6d200137-c6fd-583b-9026-13bc0798d3cd"], "h58f4cfd5g18c3g46a9gab67g65f2bd18f68a": ["<i>Dislocate your wrist, and wriggle free.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinPriest_Chains.html", "3bf0d9dd-8273-99a8-394b-2161734f4cba"], "hfa41924dg4601g434ega671g6b018f4166ea": ["*You slip free of the chains.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinPriest_Chains.html", "de6550ec-b24c-14c9-00de-b0b8684d4754"], "h9b8b58d0g061dg425agaa2cg4f216c5801eb": ["*A sharp pain shoots through your arm as the bone pops out of place. The chains hold tight.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinPriest_Chains.html", "51c140e8-2a4f-1e51-c767-0f8c8de6bc3f"], "hbeb53cfdge778g4a0cga69dg9ca46645c341": ["<i>Preserve your strength.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_GoblinPriest_Chains.html", "4da8b407-dfcd-7262-af43-dc668f279566"]}